workflow:
apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: outfit-selection-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-weather
        template: get-weather
      - name: suggest-outfit
        template: suggest-outfit
        dependencies: [get-weather]
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: weather
            value: '{{ tasks.get-weather.result }}'
      - name: plan-outfit
        template: plan-outfit
        dependencies: [suggest-outfit]
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: event
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.event }}'
          - name: outfit
            value: '{{ tasks.suggest-outfit.result }}'
  - name: get-weather
    http:
      url: "http://weatherapi.com/get?city=Chicago"
      method: GET
  - name: suggest-outfit
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: weather
    http:
      url: "http://outfitapi.com/suggest?weather={{ inputs.parameters.weather }}"
      method: GET
  - name: plan-outfit
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: event
      - name: outfit
    http:
      url: "http://outfitplanner.com/plan?event={{ inputs.parameters.event }}&outfit={{ inputs.parameters.outfit }}"
      method: GET
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: event
      value: 'date'

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: concert-outfit-suggestion-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-weather
        template: get-weather
      - name: dress-suggestion
        template: dress-suggestion
        dependencies: [get-weather]
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: weather
            value: '{{ tasks.get-weather.result }}'
      - name: plan-outfit
        template: plan-outfit
        dependencies: [dress-suggestion]
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: event
            value: 'concert'
          - name: outfit
            value: '{{ tasks.dress-suggestion.result }}'
  - name: get-weather
    http:
      url: "http://weatherapi.com/sydney"
      method: GET
  - name: dress-suggestion
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: weather
    http:
      url: "http://api.dresssuggestion.com/suggest"
      method: POST
      body:
        weather: "{{ inputs.parameters.weather }}"
  - name: plan-outfit
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: event
      - name: outfit
    http:
      url: "http://api.planoutfit.com/plan"
      method: POST
      body:
        event: "{{ inputs.parameters.event }}"
        outfit: "{{ inputs.parameters.outfit }}"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1

      tasks:
      - name: get-top-restaurant

  - name: get-top-restaurant
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/toprestaurants"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"

      queryParams:
        - name: city
          value: '{{ inputs.parameters.city }}'

  - name: get-menu
    http:
      url: "http://api.example.com/menudetails"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      queryParams:
        - name: restaurant_name
          value: '{{ tasks.get-top-restaurant.result }}'

  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: city
      value: "Seattle"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: book-movie-ticket-
spec:
  entrypoint: book-movie-ticket
  templates:
  - name: book-movie-ticket
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: book-movie-ticket
        template: book-movie-ticket

  - name: book-movie-ticket
    inputs:
      parameters:
      - name: movie_name
        value: 'Inception'
      - name: showtime
        value: '8pm'
      - name: number_of_tickets
        value: '1'
    http:
      url: <API_URL>
      method: POST
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "movie_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.movie_name }}",
          "showtime": "{{ inputs.parameters.showtime }}",
          "number_of_tickets": {{ inputs.parameters.number_of_tickets }}
        }

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-ticket-purchase-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-movie-theater
        template: get-movie-theater
      - name: get-showtime
        template: get-showtime
        dependencies: [get-movie-theater]
      - name: buy-movie-ticket
        template: buy-movie-ticket
        dependencies: [get-showtime]

  - name: get-movie-theater
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/GetMovieTheaters"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: city
          value: "Chicago"

  - name: get-showtime
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/MovieShowtimes"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: movie_name
          value: "The Dark Knight"
        - name: city
          value: "Chicago"

  - name: buy-movie-ticket
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/BuyMovieTicket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: movie_name
          value: "The Dark Knight"
        - name: theater_name
          value: '{{ tasks.get-movie-theater.result }}'
        - name: date
          value: "{{ inputs.parameters.date }}"
        - name: time
          value: "11:00 AM"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: movie-ticket-reservation-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: get-movie-theater
        template: get-movie-theater
      - name: buy-movie-ticket
        dependencies: [get-movie-theater]
        template: buy-movie-ticket

  - name: get-movie-theater
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/getMovieTheater"
      method: "GET"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body: |
        {
          "movie_name": "The Lion King"
        }

  - name: buy-movie-ticket
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/buyMovieTicket"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        - name: "Content-Type"
          value: "application/json"
      body: |
        {
          "movie_name": "The Lion King",
          "theater_name": "{{ tasks.get-movie-theater.result }}",
          "date": "{{ inputs.parameters.date }}",
          "time": "15:00"
        }
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: date
      value: "{{ inputs.parameters.date }}"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: travel-booking-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: find-flight
        template: find-flight
      - name: get-hotel-details
        template: get-hotel-details
        dependencies: [find-flight]
      - name: book-hotel
        template: book-hotel
        dependencies: [get-hotel-details]
      - name: check-weather
        template: check-weather
        dependencies: [find-flight]
      - name: best-travel-time
        template: best-travel-time
        dependencies: [check-weather]

  - name: find-flight
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/findFlights"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "city1": "{{ inputs.parameters.departure_city }}",
          "city2": "{{ inputs.parameters.destination_city }}",
          "date": "{{ inputs.parameters.departure_date }}"
        }

  - name: get-hotel-details
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/getHotelDetails"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "city": "{{ inputs.parameters.destination_city }}",
          "date": "{{ inputs.parameters.check_in_date }}"
        }

  - name: book-hotel
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/hotelBooking"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "destination": "{{ inputs.parameters.destination_city }}",
          "check_in_date": "{{ inputs.parameters.check_in_date }}",
          "check_out_date": "{{ inputs.parameters.check_out_date }}"
        }

  - name: check-weather
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/checkWeather"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "city": "{{ inputs.parameters.destination_city }}"
        }

  - name: best-travel-time
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/bestTravelTime"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "weather_condition": "{{ tasks.check-weather.result }}",
          "attraction": "{{ inputs.parameters.attraction }}"
        }

  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: departure_city
      value: "YourCity"
    - name: destination_city
      value: "London"
    - name: departure_date
      value: "2023-07-05"
    - name: check_in_date
      value: "2023-07-05"
    - name: check_out_date
      value: "2023-07-10"
    - name: attraction
      value: "Sightseeing"

apiVersion: argoproj.io/v1alpha1
kind: Workflow
metadata:
  generateName: berlin-hotel-reservation-
spec:
  entrypoint: main
  templates:
  - name: main
    dag:
      tasks:
      - name: search-hotel
        template: search-hotel
      - name: book-hotel
        template: book-hotel
        dependencies: [search-hotel]
        arguments:
          parameters:
          - name: hotel_name
            value: '{{ tasks.search-hotel.result }}'
          - name: date
            value: '{{ inputs.parameters.check_in_date }}'
  - name: search-hotel
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/SearchHotel"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "city": "{{ inputs.parameters.city }}",
          "hotel_preferences": "free Wi-Fi"
        }
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: result
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.hotel_name"
  - name: book-hotel
    http:
      url: "http://example.com/api/BookHotel"
      method: "POST"
      headers:
        Content-Type: application/json
      body: |
        {
          "hotel_name": "{{ inputs.parameters.hotel_name }}",
          "date": "{{ inputs.parameters.date }}"
        }
    outputs:
      parameters:
      - name: booking_status
        valueFrom:
          jsonPath: "$.booking_status"
  arguments:
    parameters:
    - name: city
      value: "Berlin"
    - name: check_in_date
      value: "2023-11-20"
    - name: check_out_date
      value: "2023-11-25"
